                "required": true,
                "show": true,
                "name": "template",
                "display_name": "Template",
                "advanced": false,
                "value": "You are a security analyst reviewing a code change in a GitOps repository. Analyse the following diff for security implications.\n\nPR Context:\n{context}\n\nCode Diff:\n{diff}\n\nProvide a structured security analysis with the following sections:\n\n## Risk Level\nState one of: CRITICAL / HIGH / MEDIUM / LOW / INFORMATIONAL\n\n## Summary\nOne sentence describing what changed and its primary security implication.\n\n## Findings\nList specific security concerns found in the diff. For each finding:\n- **Finding**: what was observed\n- **Risk**: why it matters\n- **Recommendation**: what should be done\n\nIf no security concerns are found, state \"No security issues identified.\"\n\n## GitOps Impact\nNote any changes that affect CI/CD pipelines, workflow files, secrets handling, IAM, or deployment configuration — these carry elevated risk in a GitOps system.\n\nBe concise. Do not repeat the diff. Focus only on security-relevant observations."
              },
